# web/dist holds the real frontend build, embedded via go:embed only in
# builds tagged -tags embed (see web/embed_real.go / web/embed_stub.go and
# design doc §7). 100% ignored, no exceptions — a plain (untagged) build
# never requires this directory to contain anything, so a local frontend
# build here never touches any git-tracked file. The user-facing
# placeholder page lives at web/placeholder.html instead, tracked normally
# since it's outside this directory entirely.
web/dist/